00:05:20.355 --> 00:05:22.269
...kesejahteraan para janda.

00:05:22.349 --> 00:05:24.250
Dia akan memperjuangkan kasusmu.

00:05:24.408 --> 00:05:25.739
Tidak, paman.

00:05:26.085 --> 00:05:28.488
